253
00:24:15,100 --> 00:24:20,037
I was sent to a detention
home and lived at this woman's house.

254
00:24:20,305 --> 00:24:21,738
Mrs. Swerlin.

255
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:25,068
Boys, this is Malcolm, our new guest.

256
00:24:25,477 --> 00:24:27,172
We'll treat him like a brother.

257
00:24:28,313 --> 00:24:31,680
