I didn't think it was wrong.

260
00:24:39,758 --> 00:24:41,692
I thought it was my name.

261
00:24:42,594 --> 00:24:45,791
They talked about me like I wasn't
there. Like a pedigreed dog...

262
00:24:45,998 --> 00:24:47,431
...or a horse.

263
00:24:48,200 --> 00:24:49,462
Like I was invisible.

264
00:24:49,868 --> 00:24:53,565
The important thing
is to be realistic.

265
00:24:53,772 --> 00:24:56,263
We all like you here, you know that.

266
00:24:56,875 --> 00:24:58,365
But you're a nigger...

267
00:24:58,610 --> 00:25:01,875
