goal for a nigger.

268
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:04,674
But why, Mr. Ostrowski?

269
00:25:04,950 --> 00:25:07,316
l gets the best grades in class.

270
00:25:07,519 --> 00:25:10,955
l got voted class president.
l want to be a lawyer.

271
00:25:11,156 --> 00:25:14,284
l want you to think about
something that you can be.

272
00:25:14,826 --> 00:25:18,057
You're good with your hands,
making things.

273
00:25:18,630 --> 00:25:20,621
People would give you work. l would.

274
00:25:21,967 --> 00:25:23,798
Why not become a carpenter?

275
00:25:24,536 --> 00:25:27,061
That's a good profession for a colored.

276
00:25:28,206 --> 00:25:29,901
Wasn't your pa a carpenter?

277
00:25:31,076 --> 00:25:32,805
Jesus was a carpenter.

278
00:25:33,812 --> 00:25:37,043
People like you as a person.
You're doing real well.

279
00:25:38,917 --> 00:25:40,475
Remember what we said.

280
00:25:40,919 --> 00:25:43,479
"Nothing succeeds like success."
Say it.

281
00:25:43,688 --> 00:25:46,088
Nothing succeeds like success.

282
00:25:46,291 --> 00:25:48,191
As long as you're realistic.

283
00:25:48,393 --> 00:25:50,122
lt's not the end of the world.

284
00:25:52,697 --> 00:25:54,756
l said, "Don't...

285
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:58,000
...let them give that boy no pig."

286
00:25:58,570 --> 00:26:00,367
It wasn't the end
of the world for me.

287
00:26:00,572 --> 00:26:02,904
But it was the beginning of the end
for my mother.

288
00:26:08,080 --> 00:26:10,514
A right cross to thejaw by Louis.

289
00:26:13,318 --> 00:26:17,084
