The referee says it's all over!

296
00:26:38,944 --> 00:26:41,276
What in hell is going on?

297
00:26:41,646 --> 00:26:42,476
Nothing, Mr. Cooper.

298
00:26:42,681 --> 00:26:44,148
The customer's are hungry.

299
00:26:44,649 --> 00:26:46,116
