300
00:26:46,318 --> 00:26:48,047
Right, Mr. Charlie.

301
00:26:48,653 --> 00:26:50,018
The name is Mr. Cooper.

302
00:26:50,755 --> 00:26:51,881
Don't you forget it.

303
00:26:52,624 --> 00:26:54,353
Mr. Cooper.

304
00:26:57,629 --> 00:27:00,063
What's the matter with you?
You want me to get fired!

305
00:27:00,265 --> 00:27:01,527
