346
00:31:17,722 --> 00:31:18,950
Give me a whiskey.

347
00:31:28,233 --> 00:31:29,894
l ordered a single, Jack.

348
00:31:30,101 --> 00:31:32,626
The double's on that gentleman, "Jack."

349
00:31:37,308 --> 00:31:38,468
Who is that?

350
00:31:39,377 --> 00:31:41,470
