00:35:02,347 --> 00:35:04,008
Cadillac's the name.

420
00:35:04,782 --> 00:35:06,443
Sammy, man.

421
00:35:07,485 --> 00:35:09,316
-You ready?
-Good.

422
00:35:12,724 --> 00:35:14,624
Button more buttons on the jacket.

